<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>بحيث استفاض القِنْعُ غربيَّ واسطٍ ... بهاءً ومجَّتْ بالكثيب الأباطحُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>و <span class="c4">[القِنْو]</span>: العِذق بما عليه: وجمعه:<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>أقناء وقنوان.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فِعْلة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>و <span class="c4">[القِنْوة]</span>: ما اقْتُني.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[ي]</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[القِنْية]</span>: لغة في القِنْوة،<span class="c5"> وجمعها:</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>قِنىً.<span class="c5"> وسئلت ابنة الخُسّ عن مئة من المعز فقالت:</span> قِنىً.<span class="c5"> قيل:</span> فَمِئة من الضأن فقالت: غِنىً.<span class="c5"> قيل:</span> فَمِئة من الإبل.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c5">قالت:</span> مُنىً.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>... فَعَلٌ، بالفتح<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c4">[ص]</span><a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[القَنَص]</span>: الاسم من القَنْص.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>و <span class="c4">[القنا]</span>: الرماح،<span class="c5"> والجميع:</span> أقناء.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">والقنا:</span> القِنْوة.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فَعَلَة]</span>، بالهاء<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>و <span class="c4">[القناة]</span>: الرمح،<span class="c5"> والجميع:</span> قنا وقنوات.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c5">والقناة:</span> كظامة تحت الأرض.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>... ومما ذهبت منه واوٌ فعوض هاء بالكسر<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>و <span class="c4">[القِنَة]</span>: شيء شبه الحِلْتِيْت.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
